arming\"\u003eGlobal warming\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/climate-emergency/climate-crisis\"\u003eClimate crisis\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/climate-emergency/global-inequality\"\u003eGlobal inequality\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/climate-emergency/intergovernmental-panel-on-climate-change-ipcc\"\u003eIntergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC)\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/climate-emergency/kyoto-protocol\"\u003eKyoto Protocol\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e","references":"\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://unfccc.int/sites/default/files/english_paris_agreement.pdf\"\u003eParis Agreement (2015), p.3.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.climate-lab-book.ac.uk/2017/defining-pre-industrial/\"\u003eClimate Lab Book – Open Climate Science (2017, January 25). Defining ‘pre-industrial’.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003eFurther resources:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://theconversation.com/us-withdrawal-from-the-paris-agreement-can-states-lead-the-fight-to-reduce-carbon-emissions-89882\"\u003eThe Conversation (2018, January 28). US Withdrawal from the Paris Agreement: Can states lead to fight to reduce carbon emissions?\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://unfccc.int/process-and-meetings/the-paris-agreement/the-paris-agreement\"\u003eUnited Nations Climate Change (2019). The Paris Agreement.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","hideFromFeed":false,"createdAt":"2023-10-09T00:12:19.711Z","updatedAt":"2023-10-09T00:12:34.604Z","publishedAt":"2023-02-23T10:51:29.874Z","locale":"en"},{"id":3705,"title":"Mass extinction","slug":"mass-extinction","text":"\u003cp style=\"margin-left:0px;\"\u003eSee \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/climate-emergency/extinction\"\u003eExtinction\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e","references":null,"hideFromFeed":f