ducts all need an urgent and radical paradigm change. We must all act on the fact that the ever-faster fashion cycles and constantly increasing volumes of fashion \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/consumption\"\u003e\u003ci\u003econsumption\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003eand \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/environmental-impacts-of-fashion/waste\"\u003e\u003ci\u003ewaste\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e are entirely irreconcilable with the finite limits of our planet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSee also: \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/resilience\"\u003eResilience\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/systems-change\"\u003eSystems change\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/environmental-impacts-of-fashion/efficiency\"\u003eEfficiency\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/environmental-impacts-of-fashion/growth\"\u003eGrowth\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/sustainable-fashion\"\u003eSustainable fashion\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/sustainable-development\"\u003eSustainable development\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/post-growth-economy\"\u003ePost-growth economy\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/post-growth-fashion\"\u003ePost-growth fashion\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/systems-thinking\"\u003eSystems thinking\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/sustainable-development\"\