 with and enjoy clothes are often far removed from the constant turnover of pristine looks that drives the prevailing fashion narrative. This is why understanding how clothes are worn, laundered, and cared for during their lifetime is key for a more \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/fashion-design-for-sustainability\"\u003e\u003ci\u003esustainable fashion\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003efuture. Craft of use offers an extended understanding of fashion that challenges the market-driven \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/environmental-impacts-of-fashion/overconsumption\"\u003e\u003ci\u003eoverconsumption\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, showing that satisfaction and pleasure can also come from lasting relationships with the clothes we already have.\u003csup\u003e(1)\u003c/sup\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSee also: \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/post-growth-fashion\"\u003ePost-growth fashion\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/care\"\u003eCare\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/diversity\"\u003eDiversity\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/localism\"\u003eLocalism\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/respect\"\u003eRespect\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/inclusion\"\u003eInclusion\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/prosperity\"\u003eProsperity\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.condenast.com/glossary/key-elements-of-fashion-and-sustainability/sufficiency\"\u003eSufficiency\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"http